name: Beastmaster Strikeforce - Agent Cincode
description: Trained with multiple intergalactic intelligence agencies Cincodes specialty is subversion, misdirection, stealth, and assassination. After his own family was murdered by a mysterious terrorist organization he's made it his life's duty to take down the bad guys in hopes that one day he finds justice. He's been responsible for taking down many baddies from evil emperors, drug and weapon traffickers, terrorist organizations, and then some. There's little he hasn't encountered that he doesn't know how to handle.
